				<div class="div-tltle"><span class="title-write">RVP01</span> <span class="title-blue">Introduction</span></div>
				<div class="div-model-intro">After releasing the breakthrough RVM01 mouse in 2008, SilverStone’s RAVEN team has refocused on its gaming roots to bring back another input device product in the form of RVP01 gaming pad.  This extra-large pad is designed to transform the user’s desktop into a smooth and expansive gaming surface with minimal gameplay interruption.  By utilizing finely woven fiber and precision stitching, the RVP01 has superior feel and durability that is great for use on any flat surface.  Gamers looking for a gaming or mouse pad that they can take on the go for consistent playing anywhere, the RVP01 is the perfect choice.<BR /><BR />
				<li>Extra-large pad for creating seamless and consistent gaming area</li><li>Fine machine woven top surface for smooth movement</li><li>Precision stitched edge with excellent durability</li><li>Non-slip, eco rubber base for excellent stability				<BR /><BR />
		</div>
